title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Focus on creating a team atmosphere where no one person gets too much shine or shade. Your colleagues might look to you today for the organizational skills you bring to the table. Thankfully, systematic Saturns direct turn in your 11th House of Social Connections encourages you to rise to the occasion and prove your mettle. The cosmos is in your corner now; you can be the most valuable player if you keep your eye on the prize. Comedian George Carlin said, Its never just a game when youre winning.
